WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 12=

01:43.850 --> 01:44.690
Young Master,

01:46.570 --> 01:47.980
Xing has nothing to do with this.

01:48.660 --> 01:50.930
I am a despicable man without family.

01:51.380 --> 01:52.930
But Xing is a good girl.

01:53.690 --> 01:54.530
She once saved me

01:56.290 --> 01:58.100
with a single bowl of rice.

01:58.900 --> 02:00.320
They captured Xing.

02:00.700 --> 02:01.780
I had no choice but...

02:04.380 --> 02:05.220
Young Master,

02:06.900 --> 02:07.940
my death means nothing.

02:08.980 --> 02:10.020
I only have one request.

02:11.700 --> 02:13.060
Please save Xing.

02:15.500 --> 02:16.500
Who said I'd kill you?

02:19.700 --> 02:20.820
You won't?

02:21.260 --> 02:23.660
When you were 7,
you were sold into the Li Sect.

02:24.580 --> 02:26.100
Elder Qiu saw your talent

02:26.460 --> 02:27.340
and adopted you.

02:27.860 --> 02:29.233
Later, because you handled affairs

02:29.244 --> 02:30.084
with sharpness

02:30.300 --> 02:31.140
and efficiency,

02:31.380 --> 02:32.500
you earned Nie Zhe's trust

02:32.900 --> 02:34.473
and became the Master of Qinglong Altar.

02:35.020 --> 02:35.860
Later,

02:36.380 --> 02:37.753
you fell out of favor with Nie Zhe.

02:38.140 --> 02:39.820
But it was not because of incompetence.

02:40.180 --> 02:41.460
It was because you had the altar

02:41.940 --> 02:43.060
avoid taxes when you could

02:43.420 --> 02:44.620
and delayed corvée labor

02:45.340 --> 02:46.260
whenever possible.

02:47.540 --> 02:48.660
After all these years,

02:49.300 --> 02:50.700
the disciples under you benefited,

02:51.580 --> 02:52.420
but Nie Zhe

02:52.940 --> 02:54.340
gradually lost trust in you.

02:55.220 --> 02:56.060
Young Master.

02:57.060 --> 02:58.420
Someone once told me

03:00.460 --> 03:02.220
that to judge a person,

03:03.340 --> 03:05.586
you should not look at how good
they are in good times,

03:06.100 --> 03:08.300
but how bad they can be in bad times.

03:09.380 --> 03:10.646
You have fallen again and again.

03:12.060 --> 03:13.366
You seem to drift with the wind,

03:13.780 --> 03:15.140
yet you always act with restraint.

03:17.060 --> 03:17.900
Therefore,

03:19.300 --> 03:20.460
I am willing to keep you.

03:25.780 --> 03:27.020
Young Master,

03:27.500 --> 03:28.780
please bring Xing back.

03:30.260 --> 03:31.100
I'll do

03:31.580 --> 03:32.660
anything for you

03:33.420 --> 03:34.740
and repay you with my life.

03:35.380 --> 03:36.586
Return to Qinglong Altar first.

03:37.620 --> 03:38.460
Wait for news.

03:41.700 --> 03:42.540
Yes.

04:14.060 --> 04:15.460
After the Six Sects were attacked,

04:15.547 --> 04:17.360
many scouts were placed
along the post roads.

04:17.500 --> 04:18.620
To avoid exposing our trail,

04:18.940 --> 04:20.040
we must disguise ourselves.

04:20.580 --> 04:21.566
There are clothes inside.

04:21.900 --> 04:23.700
You're so thoughtful.

04:28.340 --> 04:29.980
You're truly diligent and studious.

04:30.180 --> 04:31.540
You even bring books on a trip.

04:32.500 --> 04:35.620
100 Ways to Win a Lady Over?

04:40.380 --> 04:41.660
(100 Ways)
Yuzhi is slow-witted.

04:41.740 --> 04:42.700
I have to worry more.

04:55.500 --> 04:56.500
I believe

04:56.700 --> 04:59.020
Lingbo will surely understand

04:59.140 --> 05:00.580
your feelings for her.

05:02.939 --> 05:04.078
I'll go change clothes first.

05:12.780 --> 05:14.460
(100 Ways to Win a Lady Over)

05:29.540 --> 05:30.986
(Shangguan Haonan)
What do you mean?

05:31.140 --> 05:32.260
Are you trying to rebel?

05:36.660 --> 05:37.500
Chief.

05:42.260 --> 05:43.220
What happened.

05:43.860 --> 05:44.509
Chief,

05:44.520 --> 05:46.220
today's assassination attempt
on Mu Qingyan

05:46.220 --> 05:47.693
was stopped by a group of masked men.

05:47.740 --> 05:48.900
The leader's build

05:49.260 --> 05:50.100
and moves

05:50.733 --> 05:51.919
closely resembled Shangguan's.

05:53.460 --> 05:54.700
Within the sect,

05:55.020 --> 05:56.100
only he can fight me

05:56.100 --> 05:57.340
and gather so many men

05:57.860 --> 05:58.700
in just a few days.

05:59.940 --> 06:00.780
Chief...

06:12.740 --> 06:13.580
Shangguan,

06:13.820 --> 06:14.660
what do you say?

06:15.020 --> 06:16.460
She's just framing me.

06:17.513 --> 06:18.820
You failed in the assassination

06:18.820 --> 06:20.113
and want me to take the blame.

06:20.300 --> 06:21.820
So, please produce some solid evidence.

06:22.500 --> 06:23.700
What builds and moves?

06:25.100 --> 06:26.220
That is sheer nonsense.

06:26.599 --> 06:27.992
The sect is full of hidden talents.

06:28.380 --> 06:29.606
The Mu clan is deeply rooted.

06:30.020 --> 06:31.500
What is strange about Mu Qingyan

06:31.553 --> 06:32.613
having experts by his side?

06:32.940 --> 06:33.906
At the Chen hour today,

06:34.740 --> 06:35.940
Mr. Shangguan, where are you?

06:36.700 --> 06:37.900
And who can testify for you?

06:39.700 --> 06:40.620
You can't answer that?

06:41.020 --> 06:42.080
Clearly, you're suspicious.

06:42.180 --> 06:44.780
This morning, Shangguan was with me.

06:48.340 --> 06:49.180
Elder Hu,

06:50.100 --> 06:51.540
since the Chief has testified,

06:52.020 --> 06:54.260
Shangguan is naturally innocent.

06:55.740 --> 06:57.460
Do not bring this up again.

07:00.660 --> 07:01.920
It's my fault for being careless

07:02.860 --> 07:04.740
and failing to capture Chang Ning.

07:09.180 --> 07:10.720
It's only right that people suspect me.

07:12.620 --> 07:14.300
I request to go to Xuanwu Altar

07:14.580 --> 07:16.060
and intercept Mu Qingyan.

07:16.420 --> 07:17.620
What are you going there for?

07:18.380 --> 07:19.700
No one is blaming you.

07:19.700 --> 07:21.540
A real man shoulders responsibility.

07:22.420 --> 07:23.980
Mu Qingyan has taken over Qinglong Altar

07:24.233 --> 07:26.120
and will surely set his sights
on Xuanwu Altar.

07:26.140 --> 07:28.060
I am no coward who clings to life.

07:28.620 --> 07:29.500
Chief, please allow me

07:29.800 --> 07:30.680
to guard the altar.

07:42.206 --> 07:43.195
Shangguan acts in secret.

07:43.206 --> 07:44.300
He must be hiding something.

07:44.300 --> 07:46.900
Xiong Qianjin of Xuanwu Altar is my man.

07:47.380 --> 07:49.100
I will order him to watch Shangguan

07:49.380 --> 07:50.393
and kill him if there is

07:50.660 --> 07:51.660
any unusual movement.

07:51.660 --> 07:53.540
But the Chief is
quite fond of Shangguan.

07:54.060 --> 07:55.580
If he investigates...

07:55.820 --> 07:56.980
We'll say

07:57.620 --> 08:00.020
Mu Qingyan killed Shangguan.

08:37.513 --> 08:39.266
We're already
in the demon sect's territory.

08:39.380 --> 08:40.460
There are Six Sects scouts

08:40.460 --> 08:41.580
and demon sect spies.

08:42.140 --> 08:43.020
The situation

08:43.020 --> 08:43.940
is very complicated.

08:44.660 --> 08:47.100
A gentleman does not stand
beneath a crumbling wall.

08:47.300 --> 08:48.340
We must be very cautious.

08:48.860 --> 08:49.700
Yuzhi,

08:50.100 --> 08:52.180
you're saying with a lot of energy.

08:52.820 --> 08:54.140
The moon is also beautiful.

08:54.500 --> 08:56.180
Why don't we continue on our way?

08:58.140 --> 08:59.580
Mr. Mu is indeed in danger,

09:00.100 --> 09:01.089
but with his capability,

09:01.100 --> 09:02.113
his life is not at risk.

09:02.820 --> 09:04.093
There is no need for us to rush.

09:04.700 --> 09:06.220
Are you eager to see him?

09:08.580 --> 09:10.580
You keep talking about gentlemen.

09:10.860 --> 09:11.829
A gentleman should repay

09:11.840 --> 09:13.140
a peach for a plum

09:13.140 --> 09:14.100
or jade for wood, right?

09:18.700 --> 09:19.860
You're in such a hurry.

09:20.260 --> 09:21.100
Does he know?

09:28.460 --> 09:30.020
Is Zhao really coming to help me?

09:30.980 --> 09:31.860
Rest assured.

09:32.140 --> 09:33.660
I did not fail the task

09:34.060 --> 09:36.500
and have stopped Miss Cai.

09:39.420 --> 09:40.520
If she truly wanted to come,

09:41.120 --> 09:42.393
how could you possibly stop her?

09:43.140 --> 09:44.380
Are you saying

09:45.060 --> 09:46.460
Miss Cai is already here?

09:55.100 --> 09:55.940
Go find her.

10:08.020 --> 10:09.300
Ahead lie the Hanhai Mountains.

10:16.500 --> 10:17.380
Do you smell anything?

10:18.260 --> 10:19.100
What?

10:22.420 --> 10:23.420
Roasted buns.

10:25.580 --> 10:26.780
And pancakes and wonton.

10:29.700 --> 10:30.860
This one is a bit small.

10:31.960 --> 10:32.820
I want the big one.

10:32.820 --> 10:34.140
Sure. I will wrap them for you.

10:34.900 --> 10:35.900
Bracelets at a low price!

10:38.340 --> 10:39.340
Fresh mandarins!

10:40.420 --> 10:42.900
Waterproof rain cloaks!

10:42.900 --> 10:45.340
It often rains! It's a must!

10:46.340 --> 10:48.500
Everyone avoids the demon.

10:48.900 --> 10:50.133
How can there be a market here?

10:50.340 --> 10:51.380
You do not understand.

10:52.180 --> 10:53.833
This is called seeking fortune
in danger.

10:54.580 --> 10:55.420
Setting up a stall

10:55.580 --> 10:56.700
is for making money.

10:57.260 --> 10:58.980
Where there are people, there is trade.

10:59.660 --> 11:01.220
The elite of the Six Sects are all out,

11:01.420 --> 11:03.420
gathering nearby for information,

11:03.490 --> 11:04.340
so this must be

11:04.340 --> 11:06.500
the liveliest place
in the entire Jianghu.

11:06.940 --> 11:07.780
Another day,

11:07.980 --> 11:09.673
I will have the uncles
from Luoying Valley

11:09.684 --> 11:10.620
come and see

11:10.900 --> 11:12.340
how they do business.

11:13.940 --> 11:15.180
Instead of studying business,

11:15.900 --> 11:17.060
we should first think of a way

11:17.060 --> 11:18.406
to find the demon sect's entrance.

11:20.980 --> 11:21.899
The Li Sect's entrance.

11:23.420 --> 11:24.860
I can take you there.

11:26.020 --> 11:27.620
(Xue Youfu)

11:38.580 --> 11:39.420
Sir,

11:39.580 --> 11:41.060
you are not from the Li Sect,

11:41.060 --> 11:42.346
so how do you know the entrance?

11:42.820 --> 11:44.460
People of the Li Sect are still people.

11:44.740 --> 11:46.100
They need to live a life

11:46.380 --> 11:47.740
and buy hairpins and cloth.

11:47.940 --> 11:49.420
I just happened to help them

11:49.420 --> 11:51.660
transport goods once by accident.

11:51.660 --> 11:54.260
After one time,
there were countless more.

11:54.460 --> 11:55.860
This is how business works.

11:56.093 --> 11:57.462
You have both courage and insight.

11:57.540 --> 11:58.553
Your future is boundless.

12:00.540 --> 12:01.460
Sir,

12:01.460 --> 12:03.060
what does the Li Sect look like inside?

12:03.100 --> 12:04.980
I never saw their members.

12:05.380 --> 12:07.140
I mostly deal with nearby villagers

12:07.340 --> 12:08.540
and hunters.

12:08.900 --> 12:09.740
But I have heard

12:10.780 --> 12:12.700
the Li Sect is full of traps.

12:12.860 --> 12:15.100
The only passage open to the outside

12:15.139 --> 12:16.740
is layered with mechanisms and arrows.

12:16.740 --> 12:18.453
People of Jianghu call it
the Youming Path.

12:18.464 --> 12:20.420
It is a place of no return.

12:22.260 --> 12:23.100
The price

12:23.580 --> 12:24.500
must be doubled.

12:26.060 --> 12:26.900
Why?

12:27.100 --> 12:28.420
Because there are two of you.

12:34.620 --> 12:35.580
Taking advantage of us?

12:37.940 --> 12:38.980
Reasonable and justified.

12:39.420 --> 12:40.780
You do have a talent for business.

12:44.020 --> 12:45.660
Well, in business...

12:48.500 --> 12:49.340
Miss,

12:50.540 --> 12:52.100
have you lost your mind?

12:52.100 --> 12:53.700
I'm extorting you.

12:53.700 --> 12:55.353
Let me be clear.
Whatever tricks you try,

12:55.364 --> 12:56.524
this money must be paid.

12:57.860 --> 12:58.700
Thank you.

13:00.860 --> 13:01.700
You are

13:02.180 --> 13:03.020
so considerate?

13:04.300 --> 13:05.460
If not making a living,

13:05.700 --> 13:07.493
who'd choose to scrape by
around the Li Sect?

13:08.260 --> 13:09.100
Take it.

13:10.540 --> 13:11.380
You two

13:13.780 --> 13:14.620
are simply

13:16.300 --> 13:17.140
too foolish.

13:18.460 --> 13:19.300
Sit tight.

13:26.740 --> 13:27.580
Sir?

13:35.780 --> 13:36.980
I even praised him just now.

13:37.633 --> 13:38.982
Taking money without doing the job.

13:39.060 --> 13:40.006
He's not honest at all.

13:40.340 --> 13:41.180
Zhao,

13:41.340 --> 13:42.180
what should we do?

13:55.140 --> 13:55.980
Xiaolan.

14:00.740 --> 14:01.860
What do you need?

14:02.140 --> 14:03.600
It's been days since I last saw Zhao.

14:03.940 --> 14:04.780
Is something wrong?

14:05.860 --> 14:06.780
Nothing.

14:06.780 --> 14:07.620
Everything is fine.

14:14.540 --> 14:15.380
I do not believe it.

14:16.460 --> 14:17.900
Zhao...

14:18.300 --> 14:19.140
She...

14:21.100 --> 14:22.340
She has chickenpox.

14:24.740 --> 14:26.380
Has Uncle Lei prescribed medicine?

14:27.860 --> 14:28.860
Do not worry.

14:28.860 --> 14:30.100
Feicui is looking after her.

14:30.340 --> 14:31.220
Zhao is fine.

14:33.500 --> 14:34.900
Zhao has chickenpox.

14:35.740 --> 14:36.820
Yuzhi has caught a chill.

14:37.540 --> 14:38.460
Well...

14:38.460 --> 14:39.300
Master.

14:40.260 --> 14:41.100
Master.

14:41.900 --> 14:42.740
- Master.
- Master.

14:43.500 --> 14:44.340
Master.

14:51.500 --> 14:52.380
Keep practicing.

14:52.380 --> 14:53.220
Yes.

14:56.580 --> 14:58.660
(To Master, From Yuzhi)

14:58.820 --> 15:00.660
Yuzhi wishes to go out
to clear his mind.

15:01.340 --> 15:02.860
Why did he not tell me in person?

15:03.820 --> 15:06.180
You were about to enter seclusion.

15:06.940 --> 15:07.900
He feared troubling you,

15:08.167 --> 15:09.267
so he left a letter instead.

15:09.780 --> 15:10.620
Where did he go?

15:12.020 --> 15:13.820
Guangtian Gate governs a vast territory.

15:14.140 --> 15:15.000
Lord Song

15:15.010 --> 15:17.140
has long hoped he'd travel more.

15:17.540 --> 15:19.740
So, he went to inspect the territories.

15:20.540 --> 15:22.620
He also asked me to tell you:

15:24.300 --> 15:26.060
His remaining 50% strength

15:26.420 --> 15:27.780
is enough to deal with punks,

15:28.180 --> 15:29.180
so you needn't worry.

15:31.140 --> 15:32.780
Since he's inspecting territories,

15:34.140 --> 15:36.020
why would he need to deal with punks?

15:47.300 --> 15:48.140
Yuzhi.

15:49.020 --> 15:49.860
Yuzhi.

15:50.100 --> 15:50.980
Yuzhi.

15:50.980 --> 15:52.020
You can't die.

15:53.300 --> 15:54.180
If you die,

15:54.180 --> 15:55.673
how am I supposed to face your father?

15:55.940 --> 15:57.260
Wake up, Yuzhi.

15:58.020 --> 15:58.860
Yuzhi.

15:59.060 --> 16:00.020
Wake up.

16:03.860 --> 16:04.740
Lingbo,

16:06.500 --> 16:07.340
I'm sorry.

16:20.340 --> 16:22.220
I wonder whether Zhao
has found Chang Ning.

16:23.820 --> 16:24.660
Chickenpox

16:25.380 --> 16:26.220
is contagious.

16:27.260 --> 16:28.340
She can't go out.

16:32.220 --> 16:33.980
Master.

16:34.380 --> 16:35.220
Why is Zhao ill?

16:35.420 --> 16:36.500
Chickenpox is contagious.

16:36.660 --> 16:37.740
Then why are you here?

16:40.100 --> 16:41.820
I was worried about Zhao,

16:42.260 --> 16:43.246
so I came to take a look.

16:45.140 --> 16:46.660
Master,

16:46.660 --> 16:47.980
chickenpox is contagious.

16:48.139 --> 16:49.468
Why not wait until Zhao recovers?

16:49.479 --> 16:50.759
Then I will have her go see you.

16:58.300 --> 16:59.420
Zhao is usually someone

16:59.420 --> 17:01.380
who sits and lies down

17:01.380 --> 17:02.620
whenever she can.

17:02.980 --> 17:04.540
When has she ever sat so straight?

17:05.220 --> 17:06.060
Also,

17:07.020 --> 17:09.180
she's holding Eighteen Years Waiting.

17:09.620 --> 17:11.380
She hates it the most,

17:11.700 --> 17:13.580
saying Li Baochuan
is foolish and stupid.

17:13.820 --> 17:15.220
How could she be so absorbed in it?

17:17.860 --> 17:18.700
Feicui.

17:23.700 --> 17:24.580
Tell me.

17:24.580 --> 17:25.420
Where are Zhao

17:25.740 --> 17:26.860
and Yuzhi now?

17:27.380 --> 17:32.020
(Hanhai Nightmares)

17:59.726 --> 18:01.032
Abnormality is demonic in nature.

18:01.260 --> 18:02.940
Do not let anything approach.

18:50.860 --> 18:52.500
Manager Cai.

18:53.900 --> 18:55.460
Manager Zhao?

19:09.060 --> 19:09.980
Manager Zhao.

19:11.700 --> 19:12.900
(Cold Moon Blade)

19:13.140 --> 19:14.140
Manager.

19:16.540 --> 19:18.060
Qingyan, what is it?

19:18.620 --> 19:20.940
Following your brilliant strategies,

19:21.140 --> 19:22.760
we've worked hard and refined ourselves,

19:22.820 --> 19:24.220
and truly turned Luoying Town

19:24.220 --> 19:26.780
into the most prosperous market
in the neighborhood.

19:28.980 --> 19:29.820
Good.

19:29.820 --> 19:30.780
Very good.

19:31.100 --> 19:31.940
The ledger.

19:36.940 --> 19:37.940
Here. Open your mouth.

19:41.980 --> 19:42.820
Lately,

19:42.980 --> 19:44.133
you've grown more perceptive.

19:46.060 --> 19:47.900
You saved my life

19:48.380 --> 19:49.780
and even took me in as a follower.

19:49.980 --> 19:52.100
To repay such kindness,

19:52.460 --> 19:55.660
I can only try my best to serve you.

19:55.730 --> 19:56.580
From now on,

19:56.580 --> 19:58.220
you will follow me.

19:58.220 --> 20:00.300
You'll surely have an amazing life.

20:00.820 --> 20:02.340
Thank you, Manager Cai.

21:19.060 --> 21:20.580
Yuzhi has gone mad?

21:21.860 --> 21:22.700
Yuzhi!

21:23.580 --> 21:24.620
Yuzhi!

21:26.140 --> 21:26.980
Yuzhi!

21:27.380 --> 21:28.220
Yuzhi!

21:32.820 --> 21:33.660
You slapped me again?

21:34.380 --> 21:35.220
Yuzhi,

21:35.620 --> 21:36.740
I couldn't wake up.

21:37.100 --> 21:38.100
What did you dream about?

21:38.820 --> 21:39.660
I...

21:39.980 --> 21:42.220
I dreamed that I became a butterfly
and flew away.

21:42.220 --> 21:43.060
Me, too.

21:46.533 --> 21:47.793
These butterflies are poisonous.

21:49.060 --> 21:50.300
It seems we were both affected.

22:03.340 --> 22:04.660
I think my aunt once told me

22:04.671 --> 22:06.289
this is called the Nightmare Butterfly.

22:06.300 --> 22:08.140
It was born from Zhuang Zhou's dream.

22:08.700 --> 22:09.580
It feeds in dreams,

22:09.733 --> 22:11.166
more dangerous than the Guming Moth.

22:11.311 --> 22:13.646
It must've been Uncle Cheng's amulet
that saved our lives.

22:13.740 --> 22:15.553
Otherwise, we would've died
in the nightmare.

22:15.980 --> 22:17.300
The demon sect is full of tricks.

22:27.340 --> 22:28.180
Run!

22:46.020 --> 22:46.860
Lord Song,

22:47.288 --> 22:48.208
if we travel like this,

22:48.219 --> 22:50.769
it'll take at least half a month
to reach the Hanhai Mountains.

22:50.780 --> 22:51.969
Why not switch to fast horses?

22:51.980 --> 22:53.660
Why the rush?

22:54.540 --> 22:57.700
It's not a bad thing for young people
to experience the world.

22:58.613 --> 23:00.379
But Mr. Song is heading
into the demon sect.

23:01.780 --> 23:02.853
This time, my son managed

23:02.864 --> 23:05.260
to secretly take Zhao away.

23:05.620 --> 23:07.500
That brings glory to our Guangtian Gate.

23:08.100 --> 23:09.026
As for where they went,

23:09.166 --> 23:10.220
it does not matter at all.

23:11.220 --> 23:12.140
This time,

23:12.260 --> 23:14.980
Yuzhi has really made me proud.

23:18.140 --> 23:19.980
The 100 Ways to Win a Lady Over

23:19.980 --> 23:22.340
that I gave him truly worked.

23:26.060 --> 23:26.900
What is going on?

23:27.060 --> 23:28.300
Lord Song, a pigeon message.

23:33.060 --> 23:36.420
(Please join me to protect the kids.)

23:36.980 --> 23:37.820
Lord Song,

23:38.380 --> 23:39.420
Lord Qi has arrived.

23:45.140 --> 23:48.180
(Toxins Abyss)

24:01.780 --> 24:03.060
This place is filled with poison.

24:04.020 --> 24:04.860
Yuzhi,

24:05.059 --> 24:06.559
you should protect yourself as well.

24:07.020 --> 24:07.860
No.

24:35.380 --> 24:36.220
Let's go.

25:10.620 --> 25:11.460
Run!

25:53.860 --> 25:54.740
Stop!

25:59.220 --> 26:00.660
It is that heinous swindler.

26:03.900 --> 26:05.340
The Demonic Camp.

26:05.933 --> 26:06.860
I take the left three.

26:06.860 --> 26:07.819
You take the right two.

27:09.170 --> 27:10.020
Sir,

27:10.020 --> 27:11.940
fortune turns in cycles.

27:18.620 --> 27:20.260
I finally found you.

27:24.620 --> 27:26.620
What happened to you two?

27:29.860 --> 27:31.260
Let us first wash our faces

27:31.940 --> 27:32.780
and have a meal.

27:35.060 --> 27:38.940
(Li Sect's village, Peace and Plenty)

27:39.990 --> 27:40.860
You're back?

27:40.860 --> 27:41.700
Yeah.

27:42.900 --> 27:43.740
Welcome back.

27:44.070 --> 27:44.940
Welcome back.

27:44.940 --> 27:45.980
- Ms. Li.
- Youfu is back.

27:48.260 --> 27:49.660
So, the demon sect is like this.

27:49.980 --> 27:51.620
- Uncle.
- Welcome back.

27:51.620 --> 27:53.046
Perhaps, like the nightmare fields,

27:53.420 --> 27:54.820
it looks picturesque on the surface

27:55.460 --> 27:57.020
but hides deadly danger beneath.

27:57.020 --> 27:57.860
I'm back.

27:58.580 --> 27:59.420
Youfu, you're back.

27:59.420 --> 28:00.820
- Yeah.
- Welcome back.

28:00.980 --> 28:01.820
Uncle Xue!

28:02.940 --> 28:04.300
- Uncle Xue.
- Uncle Xue.

28:04.540 --> 28:05.460
Come on.

28:05.460 --> 28:06.300
Hold out your hands.

28:06.370 --> 28:07.240
Yours.

28:07.260 --> 28:08.870
- And yours.
- Thanks.

28:08.880 --> 28:09.800
Yours.

28:09.810 --> 28:10.660
- Thanks.
- Yours.

28:10.680 --> 28:12.100
- Thanks.
- Go play.

28:28.500 --> 28:30.980
Do not blame me.

28:31.340 --> 28:33.460
The journey was too dangerous.

28:33.700 --> 28:35.740
I could tell you two are good people,

28:35.980 --> 28:36.820
so I deliberately

28:36.940 --> 28:38.540
sent you back.

28:39.180 --> 28:40.020
Does that mean

28:40.460 --> 28:41.620
we should thank you instead?

28:41.620 --> 28:42.460
No need.

28:42.900 --> 28:45.740
Upholding justice is our duty.

28:49.540 --> 28:50.380
Uncle Xue,

28:50.580 --> 28:51.580
you're quite shameless.

28:51.980 --> 28:53.353
You truly are cut out for business.

28:55.460 --> 28:56.940
Where is my golden silk armor?

29:00.340 --> 29:02.420
After we fell into the water,
you took our bundle.

29:03.700 --> 29:04.860
Does it fit you well?

29:07.860 --> 29:08.786
What golden silk armor?

29:11.853 --> 29:13.719
You were hit by throwing darts
and did not die.

29:14.300 --> 29:16.540
Was it not my golden silk armor
that blocked it for you?

29:18.820 --> 29:19.660
However,

29:20.340 --> 29:22.100
your sickle also saved my life.

29:22.380 --> 29:23.940
Let us call it even.

29:24.220 --> 29:25.421
I will not pursue the matter

29:25.432 --> 29:26.806
of you abandoning us midway.

29:26.967 --> 29:28.796
But that golden silk armor
is meant as a gift.

29:28.980 --> 29:29.900
Return it now.

29:33.020 --> 29:34.300
I also stewed chicken soup.

29:34.300 --> 29:35.140
I will go bring it.

29:38.573 --> 29:39.540
Is the golden silk armor

29:39.940 --> 29:41.100
for Mr. Mu?

29:42.100 --> 29:43.660
He once risked his life to save me.

29:44.586 --> 29:46.060
This is my way of returning the favor.

29:48.820 --> 29:52.420
(Qinglong Altar)

29:52.420 --> 29:53.820
(Bliss Palace)

29:54.580 --> 29:55.420
Young Master.

29:55.740 --> 29:56.606
Father planned ahead

29:56.617 --> 29:58.826
and ordered us to dig
several secret tunnels years ago.

29:59.253 --> 30:00.633
If we leave through those tunnels,

30:01.220 --> 30:02.700
we can avoid all checkpoints

30:02.906 --> 30:04.180
and go straight to Bliss Palace.

30:04.180 --> 30:05.020
(Bliss Palace)

30:08.860 --> 30:10.860
(Xuanwu Altar)

30:11.013 --> 30:12.900
But this time,
I want to take a different path.

30:14.380 --> 30:15.220
Guanyue,

30:15.340 --> 30:16.780
do you know

30:16.780 --> 30:18.300
how to clean a filthy room?

30:20.020 --> 30:20.860
How?

30:21.060 --> 30:21.900
I once thought

30:22.220 --> 30:24.260
that all it took was
to replace the owner.

30:25.060 --> 30:26.100
But later, I realized

30:27.180 --> 30:29.780
the room was not merely filthy.

30:30.100 --> 30:31.540
Even the foundation and beams

30:32.340 --> 30:34.900
have long been eaten away
by snakes and rats.

30:35.380 --> 30:37.300
The best way to clean a room

30:37.940 --> 30:38.940
is not to clean it,

30:40.460 --> 30:42.020
but to burn it down with one fire

30:43.620 --> 30:44.540
and rebuild it anew.

30:45.580 --> 30:46.980
Are you saying...?

30:49.820 --> 30:51.500
This time, I'll slaughter my way

30:52.220 --> 30:53.193
through the Youming Path,

30:53.860 --> 30:54.700
step by step,

30:56.180 --> 30:57.420
to Bliss Palace.

30:58.420 --> 30:59.260
We'll fight?

31:00.020 --> 31:00.980
What about Xing?

31:01.180 --> 31:02.260
Master You, rest assured.

31:03.460 --> 31:04.820
Xing's whereabouts

31:06.140 --> 31:07.060
have been found.

31:14.420 --> 31:15.260
Here.

31:20.690 --> 31:21.540
My...

31:21.540 --> 31:22.420
Well.

31:22.620 --> 31:25.100
How did you get
through the nightmare fields?

31:25.740 --> 31:27.060
Since it appeared,

31:27.240 --> 31:29.273
very few people have been able
to reach this place.

31:29.326 --> 31:31.049
The nightmare fields
were not always there.

31:31.180 --> 31:32.373
They appeared in recent years.

31:32.820 --> 31:33.660
It was said to be

31:33.933 --> 31:35.740
to prevent the Six Sects
from causing trouble.

31:36.540 --> 31:37.820
I was lucky.

31:38.220 --> 31:39.500
When I first arrived here,

31:39.740 --> 31:40.580
my childhood friend

31:40.580 --> 31:41.420
gave me a sachet

31:41.620 --> 31:43.420
to ward off poisonous insects and ants.

31:43.660 --> 31:45.260
That is how I could come and go freely.

31:45.820 --> 31:47.420
So, you are not a local?

31:47.420 --> 31:48.260
No.

31:48.580 --> 31:50.620
I came here 17 or 18 years ago.

31:51.340 --> 31:53.380
Life in the Li Sect used to be good.

31:53.740 --> 31:55.660
Everyone lived honestly and peacefully.

31:56.060 --> 31:58.100
But lately, they somehow started

31:59.540 --> 32:01.580
to seize able-bodied men
to repair Bliss Palace

32:02.180 --> 32:03.060
or force hunters

32:03.060 --> 32:05.700
to risk their lives
to gather Shanci Mushrooms.

32:06.820 --> 32:08.340
They are all deadly jobs.

32:08.660 --> 32:10.100
Shanci Mushrooms are toxic, right?

32:10.620 --> 32:11.460
What are they for?

32:11.620 --> 32:12.460
No idea.

32:13.220 --> 32:14.900
I was in a hurry to deliver them,

32:15.180 --> 32:16.820
so I risked going into the forest.

32:17.220 --> 32:18.900
I never expected to run

32:20.180 --> 32:21.020
into Black Slayers.

32:21.340 --> 32:22.180
Youfu,

32:23.100 --> 32:24.460
tell your guests to come out.

32:26.353 --> 32:27.866
- Why bring outsiders here?
- Exactly.

32:28.720 --> 32:29.793
He brought outsiders here.

32:29.940 --> 32:30.780
Youfu,

32:31.260 --> 32:33.420
you should know the village rules.

32:33.700 --> 32:35.140
No outsiders.

32:36.180 --> 32:37.020
Village Chief,

32:37.460 --> 32:39.900
these two are my lifesavers.

32:40.060 --> 32:40.900
This morning,

32:41.100 --> 32:42.780
when I went into the forest,

32:42.780 --> 32:44.220
I ran into Black Slayers.

32:44.620 --> 32:45.900
If not for them,

32:46.100 --> 32:48.180
I would have died.

32:48.191 --> 32:49.524
- Black Slayers?
- Black Slayers.

32:49.820 --> 32:50.900
Where are the Black Slayers?

32:51.500 --> 32:52.620
We killed them all

32:52.620 --> 32:53.591
by accident.

32:53.602 --> 32:54.950
- You killed them?
- They're dead.

32:54.961 --> 32:56.242
But Black Slayers are not ghosts.

32:56.480 --> 32:57.320
They're humans.

32:57.340 --> 33:00.180
Lately, many young men
have gone missing.

33:00.180 --> 33:01.940
The Black Slayers took them.

33:02.340 --> 33:04.180
For you two to be able to kill them,

33:04.180 --> 33:05.700
your skills must be extraordinary.

33:05.940 --> 33:06.780
Indeed.

33:07.060 --> 33:09.500
May I ask which sect you belong to?

33:10.300 --> 33:11.860
- Qingque...
- We're from Qingzhu Gang.

33:12.700 --> 33:13.633
My name is Feng Xiaohan.

33:13.900 --> 33:14.960
This is my senior brother,

33:15.260 --> 33:16.100
Dai Qingyun.

33:16.660 --> 33:18.220
What is Qingzhu Gang?

33:18.220 --> 33:19.308
We are from the Qingzhu Gang

33:19.319 --> 33:22.319
by the Canglang River
beneath Mount Wutong.

33:22.780 --> 33:23.740
But our gang leader

33:23.751 --> 33:25.384
died suddenly
after drinking fake liquor.

33:26.420 --> 33:27.700
So Qingzhu Gang

33:27.980 --> 33:28.900
fell apart.

33:29.580 --> 33:30.780
We have

33:31.220 --> 33:32.260
nowhere to go

33:32.780 --> 33:34.540
nor food guaranteed.

33:35.060 --> 33:37.780
We remembered that we have
an uncle in the Li Sect,

33:38.060 --> 33:39.380
so we came to seek refuge.

33:39.860 --> 33:42.740
You two helped us kill
the Black Slayers.

33:42.980 --> 33:45.060
We should've shown hospitality,

33:45.380 --> 33:47.310
but the village rules...

33:48.420 --> 33:49.260
Rest assured.

33:49.780 --> 33:51.140
We won't stay overnight.

33:51.700 --> 33:53.300
Please tell us which way

33:53.580 --> 33:54.780
leads to Qinglong Altar.

33:57.020 --> 33:58.220
Qinglong Altar?

33:58.860 --> 34:00.860
What about it?

34:06.660 --> 34:08.940
(Peace and Plenty)

34:08.940 --> 34:09.780
It's not far

34:10.340 --> 34:12.020
from here.

34:12.020 --> 34:13.260
But lately, that place

34:13.820 --> 34:14.660
has been unsettled.

34:14.940 --> 34:16.780
Are you two truly going?

34:17.420 --> 34:19.020
We're already here, so we'll go.

34:19.980 --> 34:22.140
Thanks for preparing so thoroughly.

34:22.540 --> 34:24.060
Change into these clothes.

34:24.124 --> 34:25.273
You are outsiders, after all.

34:25.340 --> 34:26.460
Better not draw attention.

34:27.300 --> 34:28.420
This fabric

34:28.920 --> 34:30.220
does not look like village cloth.

34:30.340 --> 34:31.260
Where did it come from?

34:31.283 --> 34:33.468
It belongs to Xing,
our village chief's granddaughter.

34:33.479 --> 34:35.012
She serves as a maid at Qinglong Altar.

34:35.100 --> 34:36.220
She works for the Li Sect?

34:36.380 --> 34:38.540
Yes. Many of our villagers do.

34:38.640 --> 34:40.342
They receive monthly wages,
rain or shine.

34:40.380 --> 34:41.966
Far better than hunting or farming.

34:42.260 --> 34:43.100
However,

34:43.300 --> 34:45.220
there's been no news from some servants

34:45.231 --> 34:46.257
working at Qinglong Altar,

34:46.580 --> 34:48.260
and Xing hasn't returned
for a long time.

34:48.680 --> 34:49.580
Miss Feng,

34:49.580 --> 34:50.420
Mr. Dai,

34:50.580 --> 34:51.860
is the person you are looking for

34:52.380 --> 34:53.500
truly at Qinglong Altar?

34:54.380 --> 34:55.500
He must be there.

34:56.940 --> 35:02.140
(Qinglong Altar)

35:08.940 --> 35:09.900
Perhaps

35:11.860 --> 35:12.980
she is still on her way.

35:23.180 --> 35:24.540
Go find your Xing.

35:28.620 --> 35:29.460
Set off.

35:47.120 --> 35:57.780
=Generation to Generation=

36:16.540 --> 36:20.950
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

36:21.515 --> 36:26.130
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

36:26.470 --> 36:31.035
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

36:31.560 --> 36:35.860
♪Free to wander in the world♪

36:38.805 --> 36:43.505
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:44.030 --> 36:48.320
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

36:48.980 --> 36:53.010
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

36:53.325 --> 36:58.450
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

36:59.025 --> 37:03.835
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

37:04.050 --> 37:08.220
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

37:08.945 --> 37:12.880
♪I freely roam in the world♪

37:13.380 --> 37:18.655
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

37:41.385 --> 37:46.515
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

37:46.880 --> 37:51.250
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

37:51.515 --> 37:55.645
♪I freely roam in the world♪

37:55.830 --> 38:01.405
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
